If you said any of those, I want you to come, I want you to find a place at the altar or in your seat, turn around and kneel and pray.

00:42:17.210 --> 00:42:27.063
And I want us to take some time together to open our hearts and allow the Holy Spirit to begin to move.

00:42:30.688 --> 00:42:32.530
Because the truth is church,

00:42:32.610 --> 00:42:40.644
that the same God who added to their numbers daily in the book of Acts wants to work in and through us today.

00:42:42.167 --> 00:42:52.526
And so let's take a few moments to trust him, to rely on his spirit and to get out this week and be the church that he's called us to be.

00:42:53.908 --> 00:42:57.234
So Father, I pray right now, boldness and strength

00:42:57.378 --> 00:43:05.431
and power over this congregation, whether by those physically here or by the sound of my voice online.

00:43:05.451 --> 00:43:08.336
Father, do a fresh work and a fresh anointing.

00:43:10.098 --> 00:43:11.701
We praise you and we thank you.

00:43:11.961 --> 00:43:13.464
